on soft bottoms and seagrass meadows (Miller 1986; 
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F04FF93FED5FDC1FDE8FD80" author="Le Bris, S. &amp; Berenger, L. &amp; Louisy, P." box="[308,520,583,609]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" refId="ref59988" refString="Le Bris, S., Berenger, L. &amp; Louisy, P. (2017) Signalisation de / Record of Deltentosteus collonianus, 12 March 2017 (obs. 31 January 2017, photo  3514). Fish Watch Forum, Louisy, P. &amp; Francour, P. (Ed.). Available from: https: // www. fish-watch. org (accessed 28 September 2021)" type="url" year="2017">
Le Bris 
